divs: Sighting DetailsI took a photo in the South of France, Nice for the view and later on that day when i viewed the image on my laptop i noticed an image on the upper right corner. At first i thought it was a spec of dirt but the lens was clean. On zooming in i thought the shape looked almost disc like with a glow around it. I have no idea what it is to this day
trends: There has been one other sighting in Nice
There were no other sightings in Nice on or around October 11th 2005
This sighting has never been favorited.
Summary: Noticed disc shaped object on photo after taking picture
